## Verification Plan

### Automated / Bundling Check
We will build the frontend to ensure all exports, keymaps, and Markdown extensions package without errors.

### Manual Verification
1. Open the editor, type `# heading` and verify it automatically formats as a Heading 1 on space.
2. Verify keyboard shortcuts (e.g. `Ctrl+B`, `Ctrl+U`) apply formatting.
3. Modify the document title and click away; verify title auto-saves in the DB and updates collaborators in real-time.
4. Export the content as `.md` and `.txt` files; open the downloads to verify correct content formatting.
5. Resize the browser to mobile width and verify collaborative indicators collapse beautifully.
6. Delete all documents from the dashboard and verify the empty-state template is visible.
